metadata.name: Orientalist Folk - Turkey Zeybek 001
metadata.description:
""Please turn up the volume"" 

Kerimoglu Zeybegi is a famous folk song that takes place in 1901 and is about an event in which Kerimoglu Eyup, from Mugla's Yesilyurt town, is the hero. The event that the song is about resulted in the death of Kerimoglu Eyup and the house where he was killed is located in the town of Yerkesik, near Mugla.

Format : 1920 x 1080 video, 300 dpi, 30 second
